Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we have let those damned fragments do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, the powers of darkness are embracing me... {imo no Ahh, }
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels very nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liselotte Wreckmeister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you went so far as to discard your original body to seal me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an evil aura... My body is warning me to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Witch of Babylon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka... What have you done...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:36.36,EP-Title,Typeset,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8\fscx80\fscy80\fad(486,0)\t(0,1028,\blur0\fscx100\fscy100\shad3)\t(1029,1030,\bord0.1)\t(1653,3989,\shad12\blur5)\pos(625,514)}The Choice Called Ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall grant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Voidstone Fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka, open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUKA!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master of the Aeon's Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entrust your powers to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall become the one who brought ruin to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall crush all of your malicious desires to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot afford to give her more power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That black knight did this in order not to give Liselotte any more fragments or the Aeon's Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring us back! Bring us back to the Crimson Night where Yuka is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka! Yuka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But Yuka is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a fellow member of the Holy Ministry of the Index Librorum Prohibitorum, I shall fight alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your fragment comes too close to falling in Liselotte's hands, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will end my own life.{asa: changed}{err context is that she'll kill herself if she's about to get her fragment stolen}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is useless. Once the Descent to Hell begins, your lives will all be but forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka's artificial world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Seven Voidstone Fragments were dispersed to seven parallel worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but once the black moon made its appearance, all the fragments gathered to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that world still exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Yuka's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa's rampage occurred in Yuka's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not decisive proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check whether or not Yuka exists in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Tadashi? Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, about that... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! Yuka... Do you know Minase Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you already over the phone, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we do. She's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, she's more your beloved honey toast than a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dear little piggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meant "sweet honey", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's "little kitty".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai, this really is Yuka's world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm not following you on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, did you hit your head somewhere or eat something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope that she is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Kakeru's wish, after all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Georgius...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest land dragon with the power to inflict absolute terror upon its victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will obliterate the Descent to Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you, the Witch of Babylon, with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools! The ones who will perish shall be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:21.29,11eyes - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fnBrushstroke Plain\b1\c&H000000&\fs96\move(680,627,680,93)}Abandon\h\h\h\h\h\N\N all \N\Nhope, \N\Nye \N\Nwho \N\Nenter \N\Nhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there nothing we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we do nothing but wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liselotte has yet to collect all the Voidstone Fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are fragments that have already been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Liselotte's power is not as it was 64 years ago with her battle against the black knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder. Few of those black knights actually remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is all our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've no choice but to pray for their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two remaining black knights and Shiori would be fighting her in the Crimson Night right about now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What only Kakeru and I can do now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Voidstone Fragment... is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abraxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guardian angel of Satsuki Kukuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the one who took her own life seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many weaklings you call on, \Nyour destruction is still guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Writhe and struggle in your hatred and lost wishes... and then die in the depths of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka's world still exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that that's the proof Yuka still lives.{asa: changed}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This black moon is the gate of darkness that's threatening to swallow everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go the Crimson Night and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru. The next time we are called to the Crimson Night,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it means that Shiori and the black knights have failed, and Liselotte is trying to get her hands on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liselotte is after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She cannot perform the Descent to Hell without all \Nseven fragments. She requires the Aeon's Eye now.{asa: added "now"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes, then the two of us must somehow overcome her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, neither of us has the power to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such futile attempts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not from the Holy Ministry of the Index Librorum Prohibitorum, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avaritia-sama, deliver her judgment!{asa: changed}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Superbia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't win against Liselotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A way to rapidly increase our powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is performed by bonding a man and a woman who both have Kusakabe blood running in their veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonding...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intercourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sexual{\i0} intercourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, I understand just how much you value Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Yuka's existence is what fills your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as saving Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we fight to protect this world, I shall probably die as your shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that must be so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you to take me as a woman who longs for her loved one's hand. {edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a ceremony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A ceremony that will strengthen us and enable us to fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not betraying Yuka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pathway to the Crimson Night has been opened by our powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pitiful sight... It reminds me of my old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superbia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kusakabe Misao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over half a century ago, I too met Avaritia-sama across the distant seas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only repose in those days in the Kusakabe household were the times I spent with Avaritia-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle... How did your battle go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avaritia-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who wielded chains was obliterated, and the girl named Shiori took her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori killed herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone... My beloved Avaritia-sama is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world without him is no longer worth protecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact... let it be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let everything and everyone be obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka... Where's Yuka!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended it all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka... Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun... I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me do this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu...ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl lives inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a Voidstone Fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Liselotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my power is not enough to bring the world to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I require... is the Aeon's Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Verard. We meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why must we hate each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must we kill each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone are the hearts of those who love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone are the hearts of those who believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such are the flaws of humans, Verard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is despairing... It is despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer bear to gaze upon this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liselotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world like this does not deserve to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I have no use for this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:22:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have you, I am content.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall now grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kakeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.08,0:24:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, they both lived happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!{tl's orders: do not change}
